Proud cosponsor of @RepTipton bill to reduce American reliance on rare earth minerals from China—which is critical for our national security. Given that Beijing has threatened to cut supplies, we must take steps to protect ourselves. If we don’t, modern life will not be possible.
It may be that an apparent deficiency in the law has to be addressed legislatively. In the meantime, I will continue to press for a resolution.
